title: King Lear - Shakespeare (BBC - Gielgud, Branagh - 1994)
description:
Audio Books : General : MP3/Variable : English


In 1994 Kenneth Branagh and The Renaissance Theater Company recorded three Shakespeare plays, Hamelt, Romeo And Juliet and King Lear. 

This performance features Sir John Geilgud as Lear, and Judi Dench as Goneril as well as Kenneth Branagh, Emma Thompson and Bob Hoskins. Music by Patrick Doyle.

Long out of print, I'm posting it here for your listening enjoyment.


Enjoy and Seed!!
